### Test Currency Exchange API

### 1. Get all currencies
GET http://localhost:5000/api/core/currencies
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get base currency
GET http://localhost:5000/api/core/currency-exchange/base-currency
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get USD to AFN exchange rate
GET http://localhost:5000/api/core/currency-exchange/rate/2
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get Iranian Rial to AFN exchange rate
GET http://localhost:5000/api/core/currency-exchange/rate/3
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Convert 100 USD to AFN
GET http://localhost:5000/api/core/currency-exchange/convert-to-afghani?amount=100&fromCurrencyId=2
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Convert 1000 AFN to USD
GET http://localhost:5000/api/core/currency-exchange/convert-from-afghani?amount=1000&toCurrencyId=2
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Convert 590000 Iranian Rial to AFN
GET http://localhost:5000/api/core/currency-exchange/convert-to-afghani?amount=590000&fromCurrencyId=3
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Convert 1000 AFN to Chinese Yuan
GET http://localhost:5000/api/core/currency-exchange/convert-from-afghani?amount=1000&toCurrencyId=4
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Convert 1000 AFN to Pakistani Rupee
GET http://localhost:5000/api/core/currency-exchange/convert-from-afghani?amount=1000&toCurrencyId=5
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Set new USD to AFN exchange rate
POST http://localhost:5000/api/core/currency-exchange/rate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currencyId": 2,
  "rateToAfghani": 72.0,
  "date": "2024-01-15T00:00:00Z",
  "source": "Manual Update"
}

### 11. Bulk update exchange rates (other currencies to AFN)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/core/currency-exchange/bulk-update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rates": {
    "USD": 72.5,
    "IRR": 0.0018,
    "CNY": 10.2,
    "PKR": 0.27
  },
  "date": "2024-01-15T00:00:00Z",
  "source": "Daily Update"
}

### 12. Get USD exchange rate history
GET http://localhost:5000/api/core/currency-exchange/history/2
Content-Type: application/json

### 13. Get all active exchange rates
GET http://localhost:5000/api/core/currency-exchange/all-rates
Content-Type: application/json

### 14. Get current exchange rates for all currencies
GET http://localhost:5000/api/core/currency-exchange/current-rates
Content-Type: application/json

